.ti ¤ 05
:COUR10.
.fo left
.*************** AREAL-DEFINITIONER **************************************
.da VEND 7mm 270mm width 180mm rotate -90
.*************** ROTERET BREVNAVN ****************************************
.ar VEND on
:COUR6.
B47NTILL02
.ar off
